produce a simple list with data on times

Source: R/time_report.R
time_report.Rd

produce a simple list with data on times

time_report(af, num = 10)

Arguments

af

ArtifSet instance

num

number of largest times to report per phase, default to 10

Examples

af = make_demo_ArtifSet()
#> starting untar...
#> done.
r = time_report(af)
